<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
GstIDCT

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
Inverse cosine transform

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
The inverse cosine transform is used in MPEG video. This module
contains various implementations of this algorithm.
</para>

